  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Survey lifecycle in code">Read existing widget / page lifecycle code in `src/client/shared/Spaarke.AI.Widgets/` and SpaarkeAi Code Page hooks. Catalog every stage transition observed.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Read style reference">Read `.claude/adr/ADR-013-ai-architecture.md` to mirror structure / length for the concise form.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Draft concise form">Write `.claude/adr/ADR-031-stage-lifecycle.md`: Status, Context, Decision (with stage list + transitions), MUST/MUST NOT rules, Code pointers, References. ~100-150 lines.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Draft full form">Write `docs/adr/ADR-031-stage-lifecycle.md`: Status, Context, Decision (rationale + R2/R3 history), Consequences, Alternatives Considered (e.g., XState, plain React state, custom finite-state machine), References.</step>
    <step order="5" name="Update INDEX">Add ADR-031 entry to `.claude/adr/INDEX.md`. Add cross-links between both forms.</step>
    <step order="6" name="Verify">Confirm concise form is 100-150 lines; full form has all sections; INDEX updated; cross-links resolve; stages described match observed code transitions; structure leaves room for task 016 D-2 amendment.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Update TASK-INDEX">Change task 013 status to ✅ completed in `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`.</step>
